[
  {
    "text": "Even the strongest wings can falter.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, in the heart of the gray,",
    "start": 3.86,
    "end": 6.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Skyrret's will begins to crumble like the ancient shrine they seek.",
    "start": 6.7,
    "end": 11.28
  },
  {
    "text": "He communicates his doubt,",
    "start": 12.12,
    "end": 13.66
  },
  {
    "text": "a wave of coal acceptance.",
    "start": 14.4,
    "end": 16.48
  },
  {
    "text": "The mountain is too high.",
    "start": 17.46,
    "end": 19.4
  },
  {
    "text": "The sickness is too deep.",
    "start": 20.14,
    "end": 21.94
  },
  {
    "text": "But Kale presses her spirit against his.",
    "start": 22.96,
    "end": 25.8
  },
  {
    "text": "She is the fire now.",
    "start": 26.6,
    "end": 28.62
  },
  {
    "text": "She becomes the memory of his strength,",
    "start": 29.34,
    "end": 31.62
  },
  {
    "text": "a single stubborn flame against the encroaching ice.",
    "start": 32.12,
    "end": 35.64
  },
  {
    "text": "She will not let his story end in the fog.",
    "start": 36.36,
    "end": 39.84
  }
]